        <mxCell id="rOiAMbFDfOgwYJSvLYFb-37" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Reflection&lt;/b&gt;: The language model examines its own work to make sure it does not hallucinate.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Tool use&lt;/b&gt;: The LLM is given tools such as web search (Web Voyager), code execution (API Calls), or any other function to help it gather information, take action, or process data.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Planning:&lt;/b&gt; The LLM comes up with, and executes, a multistep plan to achieve a goal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 7px;&quot;&gt;- &lt;b&gt;Multi-agent collaboration&lt;/b&gt;: More than one AI agent work together, splitting up tasks (Data collection, Response generation, response evaluation, sentiment analysis, etc.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="rOiAMbFDfOgwYJSvLYFb-33" vertex="1">
